[0.003, "o", "2026-06-08 10:38:13 0 [Warning] mariadbd: io_uring_queue_init() failed with EPERM: sysctl kernel.io_uring_disabled has the value 2, or 1 and the user of the process is not a member of sysctl kernel.io_uring_group. (see man 2 io_uring_setup).\r\ncreate_uring failed: falling back to libaio\r\n2026-06-08 10:38:13 0 [Warning] InnoDB: native AIO failed: falling back to innodb_use_native_aio=OFF\r\n"]
[0.031, "o", "2026-06-08 10:38:13 0 [ERROR] Failed to initialize plugins.\r\n2026-06-08 10:38:13 0 [ERROR] Aborting\r\n"]
